data.title: Prime Video: Austin Powers
data.meta_description: In this secret agent spoof, British superspy Austin Powers returns to the 1960s to reclaim his mojo (libido) from Dr Evil, who has also aimed a cannon at Earth. With the help of Felicity Shagwell, Austin must also deal with Evil's clone, Mini-Me and his son Scott, not to mention saving the planet!
data.text:
Austin Powers - The Spy Who Shagged Me

In this secret agent spoof, British superspy Austin Powers returns to the 1960s to reclaim his mojo (libido) from Dr Evil, who has also aimed a cannon at Earth. With the help of Felicity Shagwell, Austin must also deal with Evil's clone, Mini-Me and his son Scott, not to mention saving the planet!

IMDb 6.71 h 34 min1999

16+
